text: Tartu Department Store Tartu Department Store () is a shopping mall in Tartu, Estonia. The mall calls itself as "the leading fashion and beauty centre in Southern Estonia". The mall belongs to Tallinna Kaubamaja Grupp. The mall was built in 2005. In 2015–16, the mall was renovated. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2005 establishments in Estonia Category:Buildings and structures in Tartu Category:Shopping centres in Estonia Category:Shopping malls established in 2005 Category:Tourist attractions in Tartu
